metadata.title: Towns - PWS, Copper River
metadata.description: Data Type: Infrastructure;   This data layer contains the locations of towns within the Prince William Sound - Copper River basin ecosystem. Pacific GIS (Ecotrust and Conservation International) hand- digitized town locations from 1:63,360 scale USGS base maps. Annotations of town names are included.
